text.en:
If your opponent Special Summons a Ritual, Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, or Link Monster(s): You can activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each effect of "The Boundless Open Land" once per turn);
● Add 1 "Fallen of Albaz", or 1 monster that mentions it, from your Deck to your hand.
● Special Summon 1 "Fallen of Albaz", or 1 monster that mentions it, from your hand.
